## Warning: package 'ggplot2' was built under R version 3.3.3
  1. Quiz: Price Histograms with Facet and Color
data(diamonds)
ggplot(data=diamonds, aes(x=price)) +
  geom_histogram(aes(fill=cut), binwidth=100) +
  facet_wrap(~color, scales='free') +
  scale_fill_brewer(type='qual')

  1. Quiz: Price vs.Table Colored by Cut
ggplot(data=diamonds, aes(x=table, y=price)) +
  geom_point(aes(color=cut))

  1. Quiz: Typical Table Value Ideal Cut has a table range of 53 to 57 Premium Cut has at able range of 58 to 62

  2. Quiz: Price vs.Volume and Diamond Clarity

diamonds$volume = diamonds$x * diamonds$y * diamonds$z

ggplot(data=diamonds, aes(x=volume, y=price)) +
  geom_point(aes(color=clarity)) +
  scale_y_log10() +
  scale_color_brewer(type = 'div') +
  xlim(0, quantile(diamonds$volume, 0.99))
## Warning: Removed 540 rows containing missing values (geom_point).

  1. Quiz: Proportion of Friendships Initiated
pf <- read.csv('pseudo_facebook.tsv', sep='\t')
pf$prop_initiated <- pf$friendships_initiated / pf$friend_count
  1. Quiz: prop_initiated vs.tenure
pf$year_joined <- floor(2014 - (pf$tenure/365))
pf$year_joined.bucket <- cut(pf$year_joined,
                             c(2004, 2009, 2011, 2012, 2014))

ggplot(data=pf, aes(x=tenure, y=prop_initiated)) +
  geom_line(aes(color=year_joined.bucket), stat = 'summary', fun.y = median)
## Warning: Removed 1964 rows containing non-finite values (stat_summary).

  1. Quiz: Smoothing prop_initiated vs tenure
ggplot(data=pf, aes(x=tenure, y=prop_initiated)) +
  geom_line(aes(color=year_joined.bucket), stat = 'summary', fun.y = median) +
  geom_smooth()

  1. Quiz: Price/Carat Binned, Faceted and Colored
ggplot(data=diamonds, aes(x=cut, y=(price/carat))) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color=color)) +
  facet_wrap(~clarity) +
  scale_color_brewer(type='div')
